articles.author: Reuters Editorial
articles.title: Eight people killed in Syria army bombing in rebel-held Idlib - medics
articles.description: At least eight people were killed on Wednesday when the Syrian army launched missiles that struck a shelter for displaced families in the country's northwest, witnesses and residents said.
articles.content:
AMMAN (Reuters) - At least eight people were killed on Wednesday when the Syrian army launched missiles that struck a shelter for displaced families in the country’s northwest, witnesses and residents said.

articles.title: Study finds Google system could improve breast cancer detection
articles.description: A Google artificial intelligence system proved as good as expert radiologists at predicting which women would develop breast cancer based on screening mammograms and showed promise at reducing errors, researchers in the United States and Britain reported.
